 cutscene (which is skippable if it has been played at least once on that cartridge and replayable from the main menu) explains this.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=9">tepples</a> — Sat Jun 05, 2010 3:58 pm</p><hr />
